==================
  SIB Test Suite
==================

:Author: Martin Blais <blais@furius.ca>
:Date: 2005-08-14


To run the test suite, simply run ::

   sib/test/bin/sib-tests all

If anything fails (i.e. the script exits on an exception or error), that is a
bug.  The test suite assumes that localhost is running an ssh daemon.

